From: Yixian Liu <liuyixian@huawei.com>
Date: Mon, 18 Nov 2019 10:34:50 +0800
Subject: RDMA/hns: Redefine interfaces used in creating cq
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc1
Git-commit: e2b2744a06d35ba44f32c86e0579d986931187b3
